show.description: "ISO scientist Anjali worships the dark demon and sacrifices children, but to win her 'soul-mate' Vikram Sharma during the Mars mission, she goes to the extent of bloodshed, accusations, and black magic. What will happen when another scientist, Priya, comes in the way of Anjali and Vikram?"
